    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! I\u2019m parting with my absolute favorite ride, and let me tell you, it\u2019s been a joy to own. This beauty has that perfect balance of being well-loved and ready for its next big adventure. It\u2019s got a few minor spots of 'character' that come with any car that's actually been enjoyed, but it still shines like a diamond at sunset and drives even better. I\u2019ve kept it well-maintained because I truly care about these machines. It\u2019s a reliable, spirited companion that\u2019s just waiting for someone new to take the wheel. Come on over, let\u2019s grab a coffee, and I\u2019ll show you why this is the one you\u2019ve been looking for!",
